<i>You just felt free.</i>

04:02.550 --> 04:06.480
<i>You felt happy, and you felt love.</i>

04:06.680 --> 04:08.640
<i>It was like a village, you know.</i>

04:08.840 --> 04:11.900
<i>You was free to roam and play,</i>

04:12.100 --> 04:14.610
<i>and you had the water.</i>

04:14.810 --> 04:17.710
<i>And going to the water,</i>
<i>for me, was magical.</i>

04:18.800 --> 04:21.490
<i>My uncles drank, and they were always...</i>

04:21.690 --> 04:24.200
