05:06.140 --> 05:07.870
<i>We didn't want to go.</i>

05:08.070 --> 05:10.670
<i>It was just the nostalgia of</i>
<i>just having that freedom.</i>

05:10.860 --> 05:12.170
<i>We walked around in our bare feet</i>

05:12.370 --> 05:17.000
<i>from this aunt's house</i>
<i>to that aunt's house to cousins' houses.</i>

05:17.200 --> 05:19.510
<i>And, "Can you take us swimming today?</i>

05:19.710 --> 05:22.280
<i>'Cause Grandma said we can't go down</i>
