05:25.800 --> 05:29.480
<i>My uncles would bring their boats</i>
<i>to the pier,</i>

05:29.670 --> 05:34.400
<i>and we'd run up, help them offload shrimp</i>
<i>and fish and crabs.</i>

05:34.600 --> 05:39.360
<i>And it was a good time--</i>
<i>music, dancing, barbecues,</i>

05:39.560 --> 05:44.120
<i>concerts or local churches</i>
<i>just putting on gospel concerts</i>

05:44.310 --> 05:46.410
<i>and baptisms in the water.</i>

05:46.610 --> 05:49.120
<i>Being in the sun, the sand,</i>

05:49.320 --> 05:51.790
