<i>He was just a happy-go-lucky person.</i>

23:24.370 --> 23:27.340
<i>He loved people</i>
<i>and he would laugh and joke,</i>

23:27.540 --> 23:32.890
<i>and so he was the person that--</i>
<i>to really have a good time with.</i>

