♪ ♪

29:07.320 --> 29:09.330
(motor rattling)

29:18.380 --> 29:20.880
♪ ♪

29:26.220 --> 29:28.620
NATE: <i>I think I'm-a let my dad drive,</i>
<i>or you want to drive?</i>

29:28.820 --> 29:31.000
- Nah, I'm-I'm-a let you do everything.
