(typing)

30:37.160 --> 30:38.750
(whirring)

30:39.750 --> 30:41.630
(typing)

30:45.340 --> 30:46.840
(whirrs)

30:48.510 --> 30:50.510
(whirring)

30:57.020 --> 30:59.210
This case was up and down. So I-I...

30:59.410 --> 31:04.550
And then when it would come back,
it would come back with more foolishness.

31:04.750 --> 31:08.680
And the craziest thing was
when they came down

31:08.880 --> 31:11.640
and put eviction notice on the houses.

31:11.840 --> 31:14.290
On Licurtis' and Melvin's houses.

31:23.090 --> 31:25.200
<i>When this thing started heating up,</i>

31:25.400 --> 31:27.070
<i>and we knew it was getting serious,</i>

31:27.270 --> 31:31.040
<i>Melvin was getting bombarded</i>
<i>on a lot of jobs.</i>

31:31.230 --> 31:32.910
<i>He was losing a lot of jobs.</i>

31:33.110 --> 31:35.410
<i>People didn't want to buy his seafood,</i>

31:35.610 --> 31:39.540
<i>and he was getting threats</i>
<i>if he didn't get off the property.</i>

31:39.740 --> 31:43.050
<i>An attempt was made to burn</i>
<i>the house that he was building.</i>

31:43.250 --> 31:46.860
<i>And then, uh, somebody blew up his boat.</i>

31:48.440 --> 31:50.640
<i>And when the boat was blown up,</i>

31:50.840 --> 31:54.520
<i>he had divers coming in</i>
<i>to assess the damage.</i>

31:54.720 --> 31:57.310
<i>Before he really came to that conclusion,</i>

31:57.510 --> 32:00.120
<i>"Hey, yeah, my boat has been blown up."</i>

32:01.460 --> 32:03.960
It was sort of crazy spooky for Melvin.

32:05.750 --> 32:08.990
Melvin had done everything
the county required.

32:09.190 --> 32:14.290
He had a surveyor to come in
and show ownership to the property.

32:14.490 --> 32:19.790
He have his permits for his house
and place of business.

32:19.990 --> 32:26.940
This is his permits from the state of
North Carolina, Alcohol Law Enforcement.

32:28.320 --> 32:31.760
When Melvin had the Fantasy Island opened,

32:31.960 --> 32:36.030
he attained his beer and beverage
control permits.

32:37.830 --> 32:40.730
We knew we were fighting power.

32:40.930 --> 32:43.770
We knew we were fighting money.

32:43.970 --> 32:48.530
And we knew we weren't playing
with people who...

32:48.730 --> 32:50.490
who was taking us lightly.

32:50.690 --> 32:52.490
They really wanted this land.

32:52.690 --> 32:54.950
♪ Eli, Eli ♪

32:55.150 --> 32:57.960
♪ Somebody call Eli ♪

32:58.160 --> 33:01.130
♪ Eli, Eli... ♪

