<i>My mother got worried.</i>

33:03.330 --> 33:05.800
<i>You knew when she was really stressed out</i>

33:06.000 --> 33:10.130
<i>because she would play</i>
<i>her church albums, her gospel albums.</i>

33:10.330 --> 33:11.390
<i>She would cry all day.</i>

33:11.590 --> 33:13.930
<i>So, you come in the house</i>
<i>and you're like, "What's wrong?"</i>

33:14.130 --> 33:17.270
<i>You know? And she'll be like,</i>
<i>"Well, this land getting on my nerves.</i>

33:17.470 --> 33:21.900
<i>"The sheriff has been down here today,</i>
<i>and he served a paper on...</i>

33:22.100 --> 33:24.520
<i>I don't know what's that about." And...</i>

33:24.720 --> 33:28.530
<i>So you would try to calm her down,</i>
<i>but this is just really bad.</i>

33:28.730 --> 33:30.240
<i>I don't know how to describe it.</i>

33:30.440 --> 33:33.740
<i>It's just been so hard.</i>

33:33.940 --> 33:36.450
♪ Somebody call Eli... ♪

