KIM: <i>Grandma was getting to a place</i>
<i>that it was starting to annoy her.</i>

33:41.200 --> 33:45.460
Aunt Mamie,
who has been instrumental in all of this,

33:45.660 --> 33:47.340
Aunt Mamie was the lifeline.

33:47.540 --> 33:51.180
So she was involved
with all the writing notes

33:51.370 --> 33:56.970
and, you know, keeping
all the documents intact and organizing.

33:57.170 --> 33:59.980
I mean, we wouldn't be where we are
if it wasn't for Aunt Mamie.

34:00.180 --> 34:02.910
♪ ♪

34:04.000 --> 34:06.110
MAMIE:
