34:27.200 --> 34:31.130
it gets overwhelming.

34:31.330 --> 34:32.880
Um...

34:33.080 --> 34:37.300
Sometimes it makes me depressed

34:37.500 --> 34:40.100
because sometimes I feel like I did...

34:40.300 --> 34:41.930
I haven't had a life.

