MELVIN: Now, when I went to jail,
all of this here was clean.

34:46.300 --> 34:48.270
Crazy.

34:48.470 --> 34:50.230
MELVIN:
This was gone. I'm serious.

34:50.430 --> 34:53.000
There wasn't no... wasn't no trees here.

