KIM:
Hmm.

34:56.440 --> 34:58.660
See the whole path, now we going...

34:58.860 --> 35:00.750
- KIM: You remember that, Grandma?
- GERTRUDE: Mm-hmm.

35:00.940 --> 35:04.580
MELVIN: Okay, this is...
We getting on down to Dumpling Creek.

35:04.780 --> 35:07.540
I see it. Oh, my goodness.

35:07.740 --> 35:10.000
MELVIN:
Yeah, this is Dumpling Creek right here.

35:10.200 --> 35:13.720
So, we're on the other side of
Jonaquin's Bay?

35:13.920 --> 35:15.630
Yeah, that-that-that's...

35:15.830 --> 35:17.850
Mr. Fordham bought all of this.

35:18.040 --> 35:21.520
Right here, that's David Wheatley...
place there.

35:21.720 --> 35:23.640
- KIM: Where?
- MELVIN: That big house there.

35:23.840 --> 35:26.230
You can't hardly see it
unless you walk on down here

35:26.430 --> 35:28.230
to the water and peek around this corner.

35:28.430 --> 35:30.170
KIM:
Grandma, be careful.

35:32.710 --> 35:34.030
MELVIN:
Hey.

35:34.230 --> 35:36.030
